habitat_description: I removed this species' range from Snohomish County Washington per the Washington Ornithological Society's webpage [http://www.wos.org/wbrcjan2011.html] (2011) which states "Removed from Washington State List because no accepted records remain. All reviewed records have been judged to have uncertain origin."  MJR 16 November 2011.
